Welcome!  

 

Thank you for agreeing to participate in this study. We appreciate your time and your contribution, which will help us advance our research in a critical domain.



This study involves reading a piece of text and then answering some questions about it. The text is related to general health topics, and we are interested in your personal reactions and understandings, so please answer all questions as honestly and thoughtfully as you can.



All of your responses will remain confidential, and the information you provide will be used solely for research purposes.

Your participation in this research is voluntary. You have the right to withdraw at any point during the study, for any reason, and without any prejudice. If you would like to contact the Principal Investigator in the study to discuss this research, please e-mail casobesada@rsm.nl
